{"title_page": "Va Bene (L'Alg\u00e9rino song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Va Bene\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]]\n| album      = [[Taxi 5#Soundtrack|Taxi 5 soundtrack]]\n| released   = 10 March 2018\n| format     =\n| recorded   = 2018\n| studio     = [[Marseille]] {{flag|France}}\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[French pop]]\n| length     = 5:16 (length version) <br> 3:19 (short version)\n| label      =\n| writer     = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino|Samir Djoghlal]]\n| producer   = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]]\n| prev_title = [[Les Menottes (Tching Tchang Tchong)]]\n| prev_year  = 2017\n| next_title = [[Adios (L'Alg\u00e9rino song)|Adios]]\n| next_year  = 2018\n}}\n\n'''Va Bene''' from the ([[Taxi 5|Taxi 5 soundtrack]]) is a song from the French rapper [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]], the song was recorded in 2018 to [[Marseille]] and released on March 23, 2018 on [[YouTube]], the song has 280 million views.\n\n== Music video ==\n\nThe song was released on [[YouTube]] on March 23, 2018 by l'Alg\u00e9rino, the single is from the Taxi 5 soundtrack, as on April 2020 the song combined 280 million views.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZMwbswoUdP8|title=L'Alg\u00e9rino - Va Bene [Clip Officiel B.O. Taxi 5]}}</ref>\n\n== Charts ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\" | Peak<br>position\n|- \n{{single chart|Wallonia|27|artist=L'Alg\u00e9rino|song=Va Bene|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|}\n\n== Certifcations ==\n\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=France|artist=Kore & L'Alg\u00e9rino|title=Va Bene|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2018|relmonth=3|relday=10}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}{{Clarify|date=April 2020}}{{How|date=April 2020}}{{citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Portal|France|music}}\n\n[[Category:French songs]]\n[[Category:2018 singles]]\n[[Category:2018 songs]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Va Bene\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]]\n| album      = [[Taxi 5#Soundtrack|Taxi 5 soundtrack]]\n| released   = 10 March 2018\n| format     =\n| recorded   = 2018\n| studio     = [[Marseille]] {{flag|France}}\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[French pop]]\n| length     = 5:16 (length version) <br> 3:19 (short version)\n| label      =\n| writer     = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino|Samir Djoghlal]]\n| producer   = [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]]\n| prev_title = [[Les Menottes (Tching Tchang Tchong)]]\n| prev_year  = 2017\n| next_title = [[Adios (L'Alg\u00e9rino song)|Adios]]\n| next_year  = 2018\n}}\n\n'''Va Bene''' from the ([[Taxi 5|Taxi 5 soundtrack]]) is a song from the french rapper [[L'Alg\u00e9rino]], the song was recorded in 2018 to [[Marseille]] and released on March 23, 2018 on [[YouTube]], the song has 280 million views.\n\n== Music video ==\n\nThe song was released on [[YouTube]] on March 23, 2018 by l'Alg\u00e9rino, the single is from the Taxi 5 soundtrack, as on April 2020 the song combined 280 million views.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZMwbswoUdP8|title=L'Alg\u00e9rino - Va Bene [Clip Officiel B.O. Taxi 5]}}</ref>\n\n== Charts ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\" | Peak<br>position\n|- \n{{single chart|Wallonia|27|artist=L'Alg\u00e9rino|song=Va Bene|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|}\n\n\n== Certifcations ==\n\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=France|artist=Kore & L'Alg\u00e9rino|title=Va Bene|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2018|relmonth=3|relday=10}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}{{What|date=April 2020}}{{How|date=April 2020}}{{citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n[[Category:French songs]]\n[[Category:2018 singles]]\n[[Category:2018 songs]]